26
00:02:14,390 --> 00:02:17,630
- It's my fault.
- Wait. Who are you?

27
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,470
I'm Wen Ren.

28
00:02:22,470 --> 00:02:24,990
Miss Hong Bin, don't you remember me?

29
00:02:24,990 --> 00:02:27,290
What I meant is, who do you think you are?

30
00:02:27,290 --> 00:02:30,190
You're a heartless guy who always sows your wild oats and lies.

31
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:31,760
I've long forgotten about you.

32
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,870
Do you think I'll miss you?

33
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:37,040
Stop being bashful and flattering yourself.

34
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,050
It's really unnecessary.

35
00:02:38,050 --> 00:02:40,700
I haven't finished apologizing.

36
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:43,420
So it's not a serious matter.

37
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:50,520
Wen Ren, don't feel upset.

38
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:55,860
I believe sooner or later, you'll meet the one who cares about you.

39
00:03:01,060 --> 00:03:05,450
<i>It turns out I'm the only one who cares so much about him.</i>

40
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:09,420
<i>Now, it appears that he's not that outstanding.</i>

41
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:12,320
<i>What did I see in him in the first place?</i>

42
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:15,140
Forget it. I must have been blinded.

43
00:03:15,140 --> 00:03:16,890
Give me back my Chaste Jade Belt.

44
00:03:16,890 --> 00:03:19,180
It's an item, after all.

45
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,710
How was it?

46
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:45,380
She's still not willing to undo it for you?

47
00:03:45,380 --> 00:03:46,610
Don't worry.

48
00:03:46,610 --> 00:03:49,760
I believe they'll be impressed one day.

49
00:03:50,420 --> 00:03:51,740
You...

50
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:57,490
They've removed the belt?

51
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:04,060
The burden in my heart has been lifted as well.

52
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:16,470
<i>[House of Colors]</i>

53
00:04:16,470 --> 00:04:17,890
Come.

54
00:04:18,980 --> 00:04:20,340
Mind the stairs.

55
00:04:20,340 --> 00:04:22,960
Do not open your eyes.

56
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:24,880
Go straight. Come.

57
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,470
Go.

58
00:04:26,470 --> 00:04:27,910
Move forward.

59
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:29,530
It's all right.

60
