It's as warm as the spring light.

67
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:09,163
How did you know I've always wanted to build a stage?

68
00:05:09,163 --> 00:05:10,860
Do you like it?

69
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:16,090
<i>I believe sooner or later, you'll meet the one who cares about you.</i>

70
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:19,390
I have more surprises for you.

71
