00:34:04,300 --> 00:34:08,879
♫ <i>You are a fragment of the brightest star in the sky</i> ♫

490
00:34:09,620 --> 00:34:15,299
♫ <i>Piece by piece</i> ♫
♫ <i>It melts into unrestrained fireworks</i> ♫

491
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:21,319
♫ <i>Gently flickering, illuminating the Queen of the Night blossoms</i> ♫

492
00:34:21,319 --> 00:34:27,878
♫ <i>Protecting our promise regardless of the faults of fate</i> ♫

493
00:34:28,539 --> 00:34:35,119
♫ <i>Gorgeous flowers and fire bloom momentarily</i> ♫
♫ <i>It all turned into sweetness</i> ♫

494
00:34:35,119 --> 00:34:36,500
♫ <i>I am you, and you are me</i> ♫

495
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:37,610
Yuexia!

496
00:34:37,610 --> 00:34:40,750
♫ <i>I am you, and you are me</i> ♫

497
00:34:54,010 --> 00:34:56,400
Discuss with the soul shards.
<i>[Gather up the soul shards to discuss it]</i>

498
00:34:57,370 --> 00:34:59,180
Let's try another one.

499
00:34:59,180 --> 00:35:00,240
Another one.

500
